Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是夢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是我的幻覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有亞連的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得被抓走的梵得以順利脫困
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,那個被梵稱呼為"王兄"的男人究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正朝著阿斯多利亞的都城"帕拉斯"前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度4000
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越過恰他雷山脈了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連一直很在意我的占卜結果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此而討厭我了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謀略之都
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下降到高度2000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到帕拉斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡斯!要小心亂氣流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到帕拉斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到阿斯多利亞的都城帕拉斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 阿斯多利亞是我的祖國
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不能傷害到你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的那個特別的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能做為我們之間的秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的可愛的女孩特別想讓人保護
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯做好著陸的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這裏做什麼,貓小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有看見梵大人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亞王?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,他和艾斯嘉科尼在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著陸的時候小心不要被晃倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?究竟是為什麼?王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,這股海洋的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股味道讓我有回家的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夥兒今晚上街去瘋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,那是海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露還是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,我也是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海的味道原來到哪裏都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然回來讓我吃了一驚,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到吃驚的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼會穿成這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總不能穿著禮服騎馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你怎麼沒先通知我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以派人去迎接你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 因為事出突然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亞王梵·法尼爾殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪我覺得在哪兒見過他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經造訪過法尼利亞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個擁有茂盛樹林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極為美麗的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色屋頂的城堡 在庭院裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您與您的兄長在一起玩著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…您的兄長待人相當和善
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事想拜託您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 拜託我?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你儘管說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主,我希望能先行一步回到城裏去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王也說有事想與你商談
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就騎我的馬去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎士與公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是相配的一對情侶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我們也出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能來幫忙搬運亞連的行李嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她並不是侍女 是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亞連的同伴才對!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你一身奇裝異服所以我還以為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這的確對侍女很失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在阿斯多利亞可以見到各國的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我從未見過像你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我想也是反正我是從幻之月來的嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕…\N笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈帝國違背條約攻擊我軍守城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然兩國已結為同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阿斯多利亞本土
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何時會遭到攻擊目前也不得而知!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故請阿斯頓王盡速裁決!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連·歇薩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混帳是想為我國招來禍患嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為了區區一個邊境據點,你居然惹火了寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等的失態!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是對於遭寨巴哈滅國的法尼利亞王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基於道義給予保護罷了……\N這真是個天大的誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是你弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連·歇薩爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:08:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是寨巴哈帝國的軍師 弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈居然已經連國王這邊都打理好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯頓王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是法尼利亞先對我帝國展開突襲的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽說過有那樣的事!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只要貴國肯將法尼利亞王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及其人型裝甲艾斯嘉科尼交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事就可當作未曾發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟兩國有幸結為同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不想因此而產生嫌隙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣這件事就解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連·歇薩爾!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真為國家著想就快把人交出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光憊道義是無法守護國家的,亞連·歇薩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用香來好好熏一下來除味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要完全除去汗和動物的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為您加水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔了這麼久能夠洗下澡很高興,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不能自由…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太適合你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人要衣裝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找確嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你想太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我真的可以收下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然送我這麼漂亮的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓你穿著那套奇裝異服到處走動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕亞連的品味會因此而受到質疑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得她的話裏有刺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的衣服嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以丟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的衣裳要多少我都可以給你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這套衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著我許多的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很感激你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是,唯有這套衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你似乎有著不少秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒我會好好去請教亞連的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是亞連大人差人送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"請先去參觀市集"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他有約的時候每次都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等下去也很無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就先去逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後不曉得還會發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,再往左一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不會引人注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家下船去填飽肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士官長,我們自己先開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒把我們的份也吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是近衛軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我們有什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些混帳．
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是法尼利亞的人型裝甲艾斯嘉科尼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯頓王下令要你們交出這架人型裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違者格殺勿論
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是怎麼回事?士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些混帳…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?很熱鬧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從幻之月來的人竟然還會 對這種小事感到驚訝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還在幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要丟下你們不管了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈士兵?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的話,就買下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏怎麼會有這種東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以幫你把它做成項鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道除了我之外 還有人曾經到過這個世界嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?看你站在這邊發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵呢?他在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛他慌慌張張地朝港□跑去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,你是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群奇怪的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寨巴哈的浮游要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人,我來迎接您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你已經決定好要跟我走了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷□在隱隱作痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱隱作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還是別去碰觸傷□比較好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能瞭解我的心有多痛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這俊美的臉,居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在寨巴哈,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亞的弗肯已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…那天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這條手臂被龍咬斷的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在這條命則是由多倫卡喀大人所賜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又見到不祥的影像了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是你說的就絕對會發生事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問一下,港□怎麼去?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港□就在那邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請留步,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人已經下令停泊中皆不得外出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不離開這艘費沃不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵啊,你是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有著同樣的血緣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為兄長的我,瞭解你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世間對善良的你來說想必難以忍受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們互相…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,只要是生物便會互相殘殺的這個世間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺獸、殺龍、殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紛爭接連不斷,殺戮永無止盡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世間的宿命便是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切紛爭的源頭不都是來自寨巴哈嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了結束這一切而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了在這世上孕育出新的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是真正的聖戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼為了要結束紛爭而引起戰端
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西是不可能存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,跟我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去建立新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得快點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您將能源石的功率調至最大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打算要使用變形之爪嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爪子,伸長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將梵給撕成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來救我的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,讓我趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是迪蘭度嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是寨巴哈的行事作風嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並非我所授意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這種藉□…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵的哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個時候的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來您平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家好擔心您說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這傢伙一直在滿□胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是法尼利亞王梵·法尼爾大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯頓王請您過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要人過去就過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩您跟我走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎,法尼利亞王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我國將歡迎您的造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:22:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞將會保證您的自由與權利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,為了證明此情誼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想請您展現您的人型裝甲艾斯嘉科尼的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及您高超的身手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著那麼擔心,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王一定是經過深思熟慮才會那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是沙濟瑪的人型裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙並非騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是藉由打鬥來賺錢的獎金獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股忐忑不安的感覺是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架裝甲果然美得如同傳聞一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.82,0:22:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠親眼見到伊斯帕農制的人型裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:22:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是三生有幸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.66,0:22:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你光看就滿足了嗎?梅甸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:23:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這商人之血開始沸騰了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,人型裝甲的真正價值
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是得等見過實戰後才能判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派那種三流貨色當對手,我實在有點不滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.81,0:23:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如派亞連上場如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連的話,下次再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股不祥的預感果然還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.78,0:23:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那時候見到的不祥影像指的是這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要證明情誼,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.86,0:25:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以為了你拋棄一切
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.43,0:25:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是父王還是這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.67,0:25:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為有你在城市才會燒起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.64,0:25:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有預期的別離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:24:00.85,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:09.30,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:16.93,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.24,0:24:23.08,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.15,0:24:25.44,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.68,0:24:30.45,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.52,0:24:34.29,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.36,0:24:38.09,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.16,0:24:42.10,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.16,0:24:45.60,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.66,0:24:53.07,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:24:00.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:09.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:16.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.24,0:24:23.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.14,0:24:25.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.68,0:24:30.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.52,0:24:34.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.35,0:24:38.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.16,0:24:42.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.16,0:24:45.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.66,0:24:53.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

